Class Application

java.lang.Object
entity.Application
All Implemented Interfaces:
ApplicationDetails, ApplicationStatus, FlatAssignment
public class Application extends Object implements ApplicationDetails, ApplicationStatus, FlatAssignment
The Application class models an applicant's submission for a BTO project. It contains details about the applicant, the applied project, the flat type, and the application's current status. Interfaces implemented: - ApplicationDetails - ApplicationStatus - FlatAssignment This class is part of the Entity layer in the BTO Management System.
